{"tid":814064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"颱風「山竹」一半機會直撲香港","createTime":"2018-09-11T02:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T06:26:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea0fd8571cb50bcc11bc8d291e747cdf11080e8","tid":814064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180911/20496965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F20496965&d=FUuYnxO0i5%2Bxzp683N%2F9HjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a6c9f2ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F20496965&h=39b54a42\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180911/20496965</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月11日 <br />\n<br />\n颱風「山竹」一半機會直撲香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180911/large/a1606a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180911%2Flarge%2Fa1606a.gif&h=0a27b41d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又打孖風？在太平洋關島附近、距本港仍有2,000公里的颱風「山竹」，將於本周後期以超強颱風的姿態殺入南海，本港天文台昨晚10時更新強颱風「山竹」路徑，約有40至50%的機會受到「山竹」的正面吹襲，中心附近最高持續風速達至每小時155公里，為香港各區帶來狂風大雨及雷暴。<br />\n<br />\n另一股迷你風暴則悄悄形成，率先逼港。香港天文台預計，昨日在台灣附近形成的熱帶低氣壓，未來數天會西移，橫過南海北部及逐漸增強，最大機會在後日下午在本港以南200公里掠過。<br />\n<br />\n台灣中央氣象局表示，山竹現時集結鵝鑾鼻東南偏東方約2,750公里海面，預測未來持續往西移動，最快今日增強為強烈颱風，近中心最大風速預估可達每秒55米，威力與重創日本、每秒58米的颱風「飛燕」相去不遠，本周六、周日對台影響最大。<br />\n<br />\n香港天文台表示，山竹在周末期間雖會威脅和影響華南沿岸，但未來路徑和強度仍有變數。從歐洲氣象電腦的集成預報路徑可見，山竹6日後的潛在登陸範圍，東至台灣福建，西至海南。<br />\n<br />\n至於台灣東南方海面的熱帶低氣壓，也會逐漸往西移動，一旦發展成颱風將以百里嘉命名，不排除暴風圈會登陸本島。<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n上千退伍老兵成都維權被噴辣椒水"},{"pid":"a1b2a93fc299418cf058eb1a7f56ba62a07c2c7a","tid":814064,"uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:43:58.000Z","msg":"一係中，  一係唔中"},{"pid":"267eaac79a895ccabd1e73f18ad0bedd0badb027","tid":814064,"uid":9548,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"電腦分析50%中香港，50%唔中香港<br />\n<br />\n唔係中就唔中"},{"pid":"d1cfc5e83367a9d484ecb3d72d29075fb45ffc5d","tid":814064,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"267eaac79a895ccabd1e73f18ad0bedd0badb027","tid":814064,"uid":9548,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"電腦分析50%中香港，50%唔中香港<br />\n<br />\n唔係中就唔中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966eeb67b5ae3b62d8a4d1e2a91b279a714dd012","tid":814064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"267eaac79a895ccabd1e73f18ad0bedd0badb027","tid":814064,"uid":9548,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"電腦分析50%中香港，50%唔中香港<br />\n<br />\n唔係中就唔中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a366f590dff738ef216345d555799d8afcdf83","tid":814064,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"睇今日天文台張預測路徑圖好似要直剷埋黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7bfd4e48cd03ac9b66733661cb9326a403efa3","tid":814064,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:06:58.000Z","msg":"牛肉呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4197218a49510e7e4423ab66514be60cc47f1dfe","tid":814064,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e7bfd4e48cd03ac9b66733661cb9326a403efa3","tid":814064,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:06:58.000Z","msg":"牛肉呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,